RunDeck is cross-platform open source software that helps you automate ad-hoc and routine
procedures in data center or cloud environments. RunDeck allows you to run tasks on any
number of nodes from a web-based or command-line interface. RunDeck also includes
other features that make it easy to scale up your scripting efforts including:
    access control,
    workflow building,
    scheduling,
    logging,
    and integration with external sources for node and option data.

WWW: http://www.rundeck.org
